snippet.title: Nucleite - A survival multiplayer experience (trailer)
snippet.description:
Nucleite is an upcoming co op survival game made by us: Fast ignition studios. The game is based in a region surrounded by mountains featuring a dilapidated town and various small settlements as well as a nuclear powerplant that just exploded. 

Wishlist the game on steam:

Subscribe to the channel for updates on the game

Wishlist the game on steam now: 

store.steampowered.com/app/2743300/Nucleite

Join the discord to take part in the community: 

https://discord.gg/wwG5ACBQxp

Visit the website for information to keep you up to date:
